<topic id='element_patient_name.description'>
  <title>Description</title>
  <titlealts>
    <searchtitle>Data Element: PATIENT NAME - Description</searchtitle>
  </titlealts>
  <body>
    <dl>
      <dlentry>
        <dt>Format / Length</dt>
        <dd>max an70</dd>
      </dlentry>
    </dl>

  <p>
      <xref outputclass="element" keyref="element_patient_name">PATIENT NAME</xref>
 is the preferred name of the 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_patient">PATIENT</xref>
.  </p>
  <p>
For the 
    <xref href="http://www.datadictionary.nhs.uk/web_site_content/cds_supporting_information/commissioning_data_sets_introduction.asp"
            scope="external"
            format="html">Commissioning Data Sets</xref>
 it is necessary to identify whether the 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_person_name">PERSON NAME</xref>
 is a 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_person_name_structured">PERSON NAME STRUCTURED</xref>
 or 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_person_name_unstructured">PERSON NAME UNSTRUCTURED</xref>
 using the following codes.  </p>
  <simpletable outputclass="simpletable table table-striped table-sm">
      <strow>
         <stentry>
            <p>1</p>
         </stentry>
         <stentry>
            <p>Structured - two element name, forename followed by surname, each element an35</p>
         </stentry>
      </strow>
      <strow>
         <stentry>
            <p>2</p>
         </stentry>
         <stentry>
            <p>Unstructured - an70</p>
         </stentry>
      </strow>
      <strow>
         <stentry>
            <p>9</p>
         </stentry>
         <stentry>
            <p>Not known: a validation error</p>
         </stentry>
      </strow>
  </simpletable>
  <p>
The 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_patient">PATIENT</xref>
's name and 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_address">ADDRESS</xref>
 should be withheld from any 
    <xref href="http://www.datadictionary.nhs.uk/web_site_content/cds_supporting_information/commissioning_data_sets_introduction.asp"
            scope="external"
            format="html">Commissioning Data Set</xref>
 that contains a valid 
    <xref outputclass="element" keyref="element_nhs_number">NHS NUMBER</xref>
.  For further information, see the 
    <xref href="http://www.datadictionary.nhs.uk/web_site_content/cds_supporting_information/security_issues_and_patient_confidentiality.asp"
            scope="external"
            format="html">Security Issues and Patient Confidentiality</xref>
.  </p>


  </body>
